    <name>
      <text>2.7.3.2 find the value of the function (modulus function)</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p class="HELM_exercise">Exercise </p><br>
<ol class="HELM_parts"><li>Complete the table with the values of the function \(f(x) =|x−2|\) for values of \(x\) between \(−3\) and \(5\).</li>

<center>
<table frame="void" rules="all" border="1">
<tbody>
<tr class="header">
